msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: warning/para
#: xml/update_split_brain.xml:42
msgid "The implementation has strict requirements on disk partitioning: the first root partition is <filename>/dev/sda1</filename> and must not occupy more than half of the entire disk size. Then the tools will create <filename>/dev/sda2</filename> for the system's second root partition. Further partitions if available are shared on both root partitions—take their size into account, and reduce the size of the first partition accordingly; this is a rough calculation:"
